      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "index": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "customData": null,
      "text": "16-Phase Rule Pipeline  \u00b7  waf-engine\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n 1  IP Allowlist                    9  XSS  (libinjection)\n 2  IP Blocklist                   10  RCE / Command Injection\n 3  URL Allowlist                  11  Directory Traversal\n 4  URL Blocklist                  12  Custom Rules (Rhai + JSON DSL)\n 5  Rate Limit  (FR-004)           13  OWASP CRS  (24 rules)\n 6  DDoS  (FR-005)                 14  Sensitive Data  (Aho-Corasick)\n    Behavior (FR-011)               15  Anti-Hotlink\n    Tx-Velocity (FR-012)           16  CrowdSec  (LAPI + AppSec)\n 7  Scanner   8  Bot Detection\n 8  SQL Injection  (libinjection + 19 patterns)",
      "originalText": "16-Phase Rule Pipeline  \u00b7  waf-engine\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\n 1  IP Allowlist                    9  XSS  (libinjection)\n 2  IP Blocklist                   10  RCE / Command Injection\n 3  URL Allowlist                  11  Directory Traversal\n 4  URL Blocklist                  12  Custom Rules (Rhai + JSON DSL)\n 5  Rate Limit  (FR-004)           13  OWASP CRS  (24 rules)\n 6  DDoS  (FR-005)                 14  Sensitive Data  (Aho-Corasick)\n    Behavior (FR-011)               15  Anti-Hotlink\n    Tx-Velocity (FR-012)           16  CrowdSec  (LAPI + AppSec)\n 7  Scanner   8  Bot Detection\n 8  SQL Injection  (libinjection + 19 patterns)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "pipe",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
