      "frameId": null,
      "index": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "customData": null,
      "text": "Cumulative Risk Scorer  \u00b7  FR-025\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nL0 Seed         L1 Accumulation        L2 Anomaly        L2 Velocity        Challenge\n(Tor/ASN/      (triple-index IP/      (JA4\u2194UA,             (sliding-win,       Credit\n whitelist)      fp/session merge)     XFF, headers)        sequence FSM)     (HMAC token)\n\nDecay (linear, configurable)   \u00b7   X-WAF-Risk-Score header   \u00b7   tier thresholds",
      "originalText": "Cumulative Risk Scorer  \u00b7  FR-025\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nL0 Seed         L1 Accumulation        L2 Anomaly        L2 Velocity        Challenge\n(Tor/ASN/      (triple-index IP/      (JA4\u2194UA,             (sliding-win,       Credit\n whitelist)      fp/session merge)     XFF, headers)        sequence FSM)     (HMAC token)\n\nDecay (linear, configurable)   \u00b7   X-WAF-Risk-Score header   \u00b7   tier thresholds",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "rs",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
